    <intro>&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span id="yui_3_17_2_2_1460744781571_718" style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span id="yui_3_17_2_2_1460744781571_717" style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;b id="yui_3_17_2_2_1460744781571_716"&gt;Discussion Forum #1 - due beginning of class in Week 11&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Discussion Topic:  &lt;/strong&gt;Present an argument as to which approach - opposition, integration or pluralism - you think is the most ethical model for the relationship between mainstream and alternative medicine.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Directions:  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;In each forum, you are required to communicate with your fellow students on a particular topic.  &lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;You are required to make one post, respond to at least two others, and &lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;reply to at least two of your fellow classmates&lt;/span&gt; (a total of 5 posts minimum).  Your posts should be at least 150 words. &lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;The forum must be started in Week 9 in order to allow time for responses. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;To start a discussion, click the &lt;strong&gt;Post a response&lt;/strong&gt; button below.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Post your response to the discussion topic by Friday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Reply to at least two of your fellow classmates by Saturday. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Respond to at least two comments on your initial post by &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Sunday evening at 11:59 pm Pacific Time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</intro>
